column18:
You will answer questions about eight images. After that, you will answer general questions about your perception of the US population. Finally, you will answer some demographic questions about yourself. The survey will take approximately 5-10 minutes to complete.


No personal information is collected. There are no apparent risks associated with the user study. You have the right to withdraw at any point during the study.


The Principal Investigator for this study is Prof. Yasir Zaki of New York University Abu Dhabi (yasir.zaki@nyu.edu). Please contact us for  any inquiries.


By clicking the button below, you acknowledge:


1. Your participation in the competition is voluntary.
2. You are 18 years of age or older.
3. You are aware that you may withdraw from the study at any time for any reason.
